HEADWORD: Iterate
<hw>It"er*ate</hw> <pr>(⟦icr⟧t"⟦etil⟧r*⟦asl⟧t)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos>
<ety>[L. <ets>iteratus</ets>, p. p. of <ets>iterare</ets> to repeat, fr.
