<ets>itara</ets> other, <ets>iti</ets> thus. Cf. <er>Identity</er>,
<er>Item</er>.]</ety> <def>Uttered or done again; repeated.</def>
<mark>[Obs.]</mark> <rj><au>Bp. Gardiner.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Iterate</ent>⟦br⟧

==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Iterate
